name: Etherym Energy Channeler
text:
If this card is in your GY: You can banish this card and 1 other "Etherym" monster from your GY; draw 1 card. An "Etherym" Xyz monster that was Summoned using this card as Xyz material gains this effect.
●Once per turn: You can banish 2 "Etherym" monster from your GY; draw 1 card.
